Annotation Type TestMethod


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface TestMethod
    Annotation for test methods. This is the only annotation used in the testing system.
    Version:
    2.0, 01/26/14
    Author:
    Michel Charpentier

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String info
      A description of the test.
      double weight
      The weight of this test.

    • Element Detail

      • weight

        public abstract double weight
        The weight of this test. Tests with negative weight are silently ignored.
        Default:
        1.0

      • info

        public abstract String info
        A description of the test.
        Default:
        ""
